            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As an educator from another organization, I have observed with great admiration the distinctive educational approach of The Kāsiga School. This institution seamlessly intertwines modern education with robust traditional foundations, creating a unique and enriching learning environment under the guidance of expert faculty.\n\nWhat sets The Kāsiga School apart is not only its commitment to academic excellence but also its outstanding pastoral care system. The school prioritizes the holistic well-being of students, fostering an environment where they can thrive academically and personally.\n\nThe school's commitment to providing top-notch facilities is evident in its impressive infrastructure, setting a noteworthy standard within its category. These facilities not only support modern educational practices but also contribute significantly to the overall student experience.\n\nIn the realm of extracurricular activities, The Kāsiga School is a standout. Boasting exceptional sporting facilities, it ranks among the best in its class. This emphasis on sports aligns with a holistic approach to education, promoting physical fitness and teamwork.\n\nFurthermore, the school's dedication to cultivating 21st-century skills is evident in its curriculum. Beyond traditional education, there is a deliberate effort to prepare students for the complexities of the modern world, creating a well-rounded educational experience.\n\nThe integration of diverse activities and hobbies is a testament to the school's commitment to nurturing individual talents and interests. This approach ensures that students have ample opportunities to explore and develop their skills beyond the academic realm.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
