          "reviewBody": "I really like how easy it is to get to both indoor and outdoor activities here. The sports center has a football field, a cricket stadium, a swimming pool, a tennis court, and a gym for overall physical fitness. I interacted with the vice principal regarding my queries and I have to say I was greatly impressed by her personality and hospitality.\nStudents also get a huge library and professional musicians as their music and singing instructors.",
